  exerciseTitle: Going under 0 and above Max
  videoWalkthroughUrl: https://unitycodemonkey.teachable.com/courses/problem-solving/lectures/63458629
  exerciseText: Bullets should deal damage, but health should not go under 0 or above
    the max
  hintText: Mathf.Clamp();
  solutionText: 'Apply a Clamp to validate the value between 0 and Max whenever health
    amount changes

    healthAmount = Mathf.Clamp(healthAmount, 0, healthAmountMax);'
